ing. &lt;on/off&gt;</P><P>I'll stop there for now, The list is endless. Think up some of your own.</P><P>As always feedback is appreciated. Feel free to submit these to verant if you feel you would like it added to your current ability set.</P><P>Tyler</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
