>Type 'I demand to see targets corpse.' No component. Reuse is 15 minutes. (Consent is required, like a rez.)</P><P>Summon the Dead (15)<BR>Summon any undead on your tracking except boss mobs. Reuse is 15 minutes.</P><P>Imbue weapon (10)<BR>Makes any spell you have half as effective but capable of procing on someone elses weapon for 15 minutes. Reuse is 45minutes. Spell costs triple mana usage.</P><P>Cloud Of Death. (7)<BR>Makes any DoT spell point blank area of effect. Triples mana usage.</P><P>Cloud of Empathy (15)<BR>Makes Lifetaps heal everyone surronding you for 1/8 efficiency. Includes Lifetap over time.</P><P>Cloud of Wisdom (15)<BR>Gives all your mana equally to your group. This is targetable at another group.</P><P>Bane of the Dead. (1/3/7)<BR>Imbues party memebers weapons with Dead bane damage. +1 +3 and +5 Respectively. Lasts 72 minutes. Recast is 72 minutes.</P><P>Tyler</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Tyler on 07/23/2002  14:12:28<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
